I ran into this issue. The problem was a typo. I had this:
```
OAUTH_PROVIDERS = [
    {
        'name': 'Google',
        ...
}
]
```
instead of this:
```
OAUTH_PROVIDERS = [
    {
        'name': 'google',
        ...
}
]
```
Hope this helps someone.

